column1: # Supplemental Material: Transformed Antineutrino Covariance Matrix         #
# Transformed Covariance Matrix of the unfolded U235 antineutrino energy spectrum from HFIR observed by PROSPECT detector.
# Unfolding performed using Wiener-SVD method. Model comparisons require the unfolding smearing matrix.
# The covariance matrix is calculated from toy Monte Carlo tests
column2: and the bias from the input model in the unfolding method has been included.

column1: # Constructed as 26x26 bins in true energy space. Edges span [1.8 - 8.3]MeV
